title: Ep 2012 - Jethalal ki Duvidha
shortDesc: Daya tells Jethalal that she wishes to wear the diamond studded saree which is worth ten crore rupees. Jethalal promises his wife and her friends that he would borrow the saree from his friend for a day.

title: Ep 2013 - Taarak Ka Idea
shortDesc: Jethalal tells Taarak that he can’t borrow saree from Hiralal. Daya and all women of Gokuldham Society force Jethalal to bring the diamond-studded saree as soon as possible. Will Jethalal agree to fulfil Daya’s wish?

title: Ep 2014 - Jethalal Ki Tarkeeb
shortDesc: Taarak and Jethalal come to Jitu’s shop. They request him to tailor a saree which would resemble the diamond-studded saree shown in the exhibition. Will Jethalal be able to fulfil Daya’s dream?

title: Ep 2015 - Jethalal Brings Saree
shortDesc: Bhide tells Dr. Hathi and Iyer that Jethalal should not have brought diamond studded saree to Gokuldham society. Bhide tells Jethalal that his wife may force him to buy the expensive saree.

title: Ep 2016 - Daya Wears Diamond Studded Saree
shortDesc: Jethalal and Taarak bring a fake diamond-studded saree to Gokuldham society. Daya wears the saree and thanks Jethalal for fulfilling her wish.

title: Ep 2017 - Chori Ki Saadi
shortDesc: Jethalal informs Iyer that he has to return the diamond-studded saree to Hiralal. He requests Iyer to return the saree at the earliest.

title: Ep 2018 - Goons Attack Jethalal and Taarak
shortDesc: Jethalal and Taarak decide to return the fake diamond-studded saree to Jitubhai. A few goons snatch the saree from Jethalal’s hand and flee away.

title: Ep 2019 - Champaklal Files Police Complaint
shortDesc: Champaklal and his neighbors come to police station. They inform the police that a few goons have stolen diamond-studded saree. Hiralal tells Pande that he had not given the expensive saree to Jethalal.

title: Ep 2020 - Jethalal In Police Station
shortDesc: Jethalal informs police that he had given a fake-diamond saree to Daya. Jethalal apologizes to his wife for his mistake. Mukesh tells the police that he had not sold the saree to Jethalal.

title: Ep 2021 - Police Arrests Jethalal and Taarak
shortDesc: Hiralal tells the police that Jethalal must have stolen the diamond-studded saree. Police arrests Jethalal and Taarak and put them in jail. Bagha tells Police that he had placed a camera in Hiralal’s exhibition.

title: Ep 2022 - Ganesh Utsav in Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Ruby informs the police that she had stolen the expensive saree from the exhibition. The Gokuldham Society gather to perform Lord Ganesha’s puja on the occasion of Ganesh Chaturthi.

title: Ep 2023 - Bhide Requires Volunteers For Ganesha Utsav
shortDesc: Bhide calls his neighbours for a meeting to plan for the Ganesha festival. Jethalal and all his friends clear it to Bhide that they do not have enough time to volunteer for the Ganesha Utsav.

title: Ep 2024 - Secret Theme of Ganesha Festival
shortDesc: The women of Gokuldham Society decide to take on the responsibilities of Ganesha festival. Bhide asks them to reveal the theme of the festival.

title: Ep 2025 - Innovative Ganesh Pandal
shortDesc: The women of Gokuldham society organize Ganesha festival. Jethalal and his friends appreciate the ladies for coming up with innovative pandal theme.

title: Ep 2026 - Gokuldham Society Celebrates Ganesha Festival
shortDesc: Jethalal asks Daya as to what she has planned for Ganesha festival in the evening. Daya refuses to give any details to Jethalal. The members of Gokuldham Society gather to celebrate Ganesha festival.
